title: MsIris
text:
Fabulous website. (disclaimer) my nephew discovered them and from previous history recommended highly. He told me exactly what to purchase. So that made my purchase EASY.
I forgot to use a promo code and despite the coaching messed up on a dimension. Email next day = promo code granted and dimension changed.
Upon receipt of my framed picture= PRICELESS SATISFACTION.
WORTH EVERY PENNY! HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!
